    "name": "Highway to Heal",
    "steam_appid": 2213710,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213710/extras/3af45980260e9f3a06f71dfc2ab86a33.poster.avif?t=1763128142\" width=610 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213710/extras/3af45980260e9f3a06f71dfc2ab86a33.webm?t=1763128142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213710/extras/3af45980260e9f3a06f71dfc2ab86a33.mp4?t=1763128142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Drive fast and take care of adorable folks!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Highway to Heal</i> is an <strong>arcade driving-adventure</strong> game in an open world city of a sustainable near-future. Take the wheel of an <strong>ambulance</strong> to help the residents. <br>📢 Make your siren blare to bring in your patients safe and sound in record time!<br>🩹 Provide first-aid even while driving!<br>⛈️ Face storms, traffic and the whims of your patients!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213710/extras/2e8213516b0a4c1354fef6af5380f74f.poster.avif?t=1763128142\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213710/extras/2e8213516b0a4c1354fef6af5380f74f.webm?t=1763128142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213710/extras/2e8213516b0a4c1354fef6af5380f74f.mp4?t=1763128142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Leap into the action of an extraordinary paramedic duo!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ll be assigned exciting missions to <strong>save patients in distress</strong>. From the Ambulance Center, hit the roads of the hectic open world of Le Mascaret! Dodge traffic jams, zigzag between accidents and <strong>exploit audacious shortcuts</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213710/extras/c9a7361e2366b11e653725fa9b14b8c6.poster.avif?t=1763128142\" width=610 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213710/extras/c9a7361e2366b11e653725fa9b14b8c6.webm?t=1763128142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213710/extras/c9a7361e2366b11e653725fa9b14b8c6.mp4?t=1763128142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you reach them, the challenge continues: stabilize their vital signs through <strong>quick and intuitive mini-games</strong> (immobilisation, disinfection, injection, ...). Is your patient’s health degrading en route? No problem, administer <strong>treatments as you drive</strong>! Precision and a cool head will be your allies as you keep your patients healthy while you transport them…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improvisation, adaptation and determination will be your watchwords to triumph over obstacles and save lives. So put on your uniform, <strong>switch on the siren</strong> and prove that nothing can stop you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213710/extras/1fd3bb15de81f3024d9b8f8577ef4118.poster.avif?t=1763128142\" width=610 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213710/extras/1fd3bb15de81f3024d9b8f8577ef4118.webm?t=1763128142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213710/extras/1fd3bb15de81f3024d9b8f8577ef4118.mp4?t=1763128142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Discover a greener future where local community is key!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a <strong>huge crisis and revolution</strong>, citizens are now rebuilding a world step by step by <strong>empowering local communities</strong>. They are your patients and they have a lot of stories to tell about this new world in the making.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213710/extras/324f46afeb4a9afe24ef57d056d8ad74.poster.avif?t=1763128142\" width=610 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213710/extras/324f46afeb4a9afe24ef57d056d8ad74.webm?t=1763128142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213710/extras/324f46afeb4a9afe24ef57d056d8ad74.mp4?t=1763128142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Work as a team and become a valuable part of the city</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visit the various city services available to assist you on your mission: <strong>repair and customize your ambulance</strong> in a Garage with various unlockable upgrades, <strong>choose your treatment tools</strong> in a Pharmacy and access the <strong>city's most reliable traffic information</strong> in the neighborhood’s Town Hall.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do your best to eventually <strong>move up the ranks</strong>! You'll obtain the trust of your peers and will be allowed to use more advanced tools!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213710/extras/54d5bfbd1abc196390130986d0dfeda7.poster.avif?t=1763128142\" width=610 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213710/extras/54d5bfbd1abc196390130986d0dfeda7.webm?t=1763128142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213710/extras/54d5bfbd1abc196390130986d0dfeda7.mp4?t=1763128142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧑‍⚕️ Dozens of rescue missions,<br>🩹 Multiple medical care gestures to treat your patients during missions, <br>👥 Many characters with their own personal stories to discover.<br>🏛️ A large handmade open-world European inspired city to explore,<br>🚑 Many ambulance upgrade collectibles to find through the city,<br>💊 Customizable vehicle and medical equipmen.</p>",
